This is a list of the best local SEO agencies and companies in the UK, compared by location, specialism, and budget so you can match a provider to your business rather than to a marketing pitch. As an independent SEO consultant based in Reading, Berkshire, I have no financial relationship with any provider listed here, and no company paid for inclusion. I am listed first myself, transparently, because excluding the author of a comparison would be less honest than disclosing the conflict openly. Evaluate the evidence and decide for yourself.

Local SEO decides which businesses win the customers who are ready to act. Searches with local intent, the "near me" queries and the map results, convert faster than almost any other kind of search, because the person searching usually wants to buy, book, or visit today. The prize is the local pack: the three map listings Google places above the standard results, fed by your Google Business Profile, your local citations, and your on-page relevance. Rank there and you capture demand at the moment of decision. Miss it and a competitor takes the call. The numbers behind that shift sit in the [local SEO statistics](/blog/local-seo-statistics/) breakdown.

**Selection criteria:** demonstrated local SEO capability, Google Business Profile and local citation expertise, transparent pricing, genuine UK presence, and fit across different business types and budgets.

