## Sunny Patel SEO, Best for Direct Senior Access

**Based in:** Reading, Berkshire, serving London, the Thames Valley, and the South East in person, UK-wide remotely | **Best for:** SMEs, professional services, local and multi-location businesses | **Budget:** From £1,200/mo

*Disclosure: This is my own practice. I list myself first because hiding the author of a comparison would be less honest than disclosing it. Judge the evidence yourself.*

You work directly with me, a senior consultant, on every engagement. There is no account manager layer, no junior handoff, and no agency markup on the work. Based in Reading, 25 minutes from London Paddington, I serve clients across London, the Thames Valley, and the South East in person, and the rest of the UK remotely. That combination of regional knowledge and face-to-face access is something fully remote agencies cannot offer, and it matters for [local SEO in Berkshire](/services/seo-berkshire/) and the surrounding commuter towns where I know the search landscape first-hand.

The method is [semantic SEO](/services/semantic-seo/) applied to [local search](/services/local-seo/): Google Business Profile optimisation, consistent local citations, location landing pages built on real entity relationships, and local schema that helps both Google and AI assistants understand exactly where you operate and what you do. That same approach produced a documented [AI-search](/services/ai-search-optimisation/) lead conversion, a healthcare client, Express Medicals, that discovered my services through a Bing Copilot citation and converted to a paid engagement. Few local SEO providers can point to a citation that produced a client.

**Best for:** SMEs, professional services, healthcare and regulated firms, and local or multi-location businesses that want senior delivery and a methodical local foundation rather than a templated agency package. Particularly strong for businesses in [Reading](/services/local-seo-reading/), the Thames Valley, and [London](/).

**Unique strength:** Direct senior access with no agency markup, plus a documented AI-search conversion built on the same semantic and local methodology.

**Considerations:**
- Sole practitioner, so execution capacity is limited for very large multi-location content programmes
- Not suited to businesses wanting one provider to run every digital channel

**Starting from:** £1,200/month. [Get in touch](/contact/) for a free initial conversation.

